                    <div class="article">
                                                                        <p>菠萝花样<a href="/a/bzrs-jd.html"><strong>经典</strong></a>耐看镂空精致</p><p>却必须要</p><p>够大够暖和</p><p>那就细线，加宽</p><p>然鹅，没想到吧</p><p>它却是烂尾的转身</p><p>哈哈哈</p><p><img src="https://img.bianzhirensheng.com/forum/202101/10/124442l6nlnh2hxl5d5qhq.jpg" width="600" height="800" title="钩针围巾" alt="钩针围巾"/></p><p><img src="https://img.bianzhirensheng.com/forum/202101/10/124442fd6e6z6dz5qlgog3.jpg" width="600"/></p><p><img src="https://img.bianzhirensheng.com/forum/202101/10/124444yxcacjc4pc4j8zfj.jpg" width="600"/></p><p><img src="https://img.bianzhirensheng.com/forum/202101/10/124439zxw19oan1e095oec.jpg" width="600" height="703" title="女士钩针菠萝围巾" alt="女士钩针菠萝围巾"/></p><p><img src="https://img.bianzhirensheng.com/forum/202101/10/124443zwe3gipjhihqiq7i.jpg" width="600"/></p><p><img src="https://img.bianzhirensheng.com/forum/202101/10/124440v8yqz18telnj87ye.jpg" width="600"/></p><p><img src="https://img.bianzhirensheng.com/forum/202101/10/124440jx9y7417x7z194ho.jpg" width="600"/></p><p>用针：广牌 2.0 mm</p><p>用线：24/3 <a href="/t/%E5%B1%B1%E7%BE%8A%E7%BB%92.html">山羊绒</a> 单股 5团</p><p>成品：长220 cm/宽50cm/重247g</p><p><br/></p>                                                                    </div>
